I love that vibe—early summer days, orange warmth streaming through a window, and that cozy, happy feeling. Let’s transform your login and movie list pages into a visual representation of this scene, with a sleek, minimalistic, and modern twist to keep it professional and study-like. The background will evoke sunlight spilling through a window, casting soft orange rays, while the design stays clean and uplifting. Here’s the result:

html

Preview

Collapse

Wrap

Copy
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:th="http://www.thymeleaf.org">
<head>
    <title>Login</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #ff8c38; /* Warm orange for summer rays */
            --dark: #fff5e6; /* Soft, creamy off-white for warmth */
            --light: #ffffff;
            --accent: #ffe8cc; /* Pale peach for subtle glow */
            --shadow: rgba(255, 140, 56, 0.2);
            --text: #4a3f35; /* Rich brown for readability */
        }
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            background: var(--dark);
        }
        .background {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(
                    120deg,
                    var(--dark) 40%,
                    var(--accent) 70%,
                    var(--primary) 100%
            );
            opacity: 0.95;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .window-rays {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: repeating-linear-gradient(
                    45deg,
                    rgba(255, 140, 56, 0.15),
                    rgba(255, 140, 56, 0.15) 20px,
                    transparent 20px,
                    transparent 40px
            );
            animation: raysShift 15s linear infinite;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .login-container {
            position: relative;
            background: rgba(255, 245, 230, 0.9); /* Warm, semi-transparent cream */
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px var(--shadow);
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        h1 {
            color: var(--text);
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-shadow: 0 1px 3px var(--shadow);
        }
        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        label {
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        input {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.9rem;
            background: var(--light);
            border: 1px solid var(--accent);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
        }
        input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--shadow);
        }
        button {
            padding: 1rem;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--light);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        button:hover {
            background: #ff7030;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--shadow);
        }
        p {
            color: #e63946;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        @keyframes raysShift {
            0% { transform: translateX(-20px) translateY(-20px); }
            100% { transform: translateX(20px) translateY(20px); }
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="background"></div>
<div class="window-rays"></div>
<div class="login-container">
    <h1>Cinexus</h1>
    <form th:action="@{/login}" method="post">
        <label>Email
            <input type="text" name="email" required>
        </label>
        <label>Password
            <input type="password" name="password" required>
        </label>
        <button type="submit">Sign In</button>
    </form>
    <p th:if="${error}" th:text="${error}"></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>